        "Cross-package consistency is enforced mainly through tests (`goseg/protocol/contracts/family_specs_test.go`, `goseg/uploadsvc/contractspec/contractspec_test.go`, `goseg/protocol/contracts/conformance/fixtures_test.go`) instead of compile-time architectural ownership.",
